OL,3,CConcerns raised over #22m 'restricted'
OL,4,Cprocedure spend in NI health service
OL,6,FQuestions have been raised over
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's health trusts
OL,8,Fspending #22million on 'restricted'
OL,9,Fprocedures in the past financial year.
OL,11,FRestricted procedures are those which
OL,12,Fare not normally available on the NHS
OL,13,Fbut are carried after consideration of
OL,14,Fspecific circumstances.
