OL,3,CConcerns raised over #22m 'restricted'
OL,4,Cprocedure spend in NI health service
OL,6,FComptroller and Auditor General
OL,7,FDorinnia Carville said there was a
OL,8,F"lack of oversight" by the trusts and
OL,9,Fthe Department of Health, something
OL,10,Fshe said was "very disappointing,"
OL,11,Fespecially given the financial
OL,12,Fpressures facing the health service in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,15,FA report by the NI Audit Office found
OL,16,Fthat in the financial year up to April
OL,17,F2024 12,000 procedures such as breast
OL,18,Freductions, liposuction and tattoo
OL,19,Fremovals were carried out.
