OL,3,CConcerns raised over #22m 'restricted'
OL,4,Cprocedure spend in NI health service
OL,6,FAbout #6million was also spent
OL,7,Fremoving patients' tonsils.
OL,9,FThe report looks at the Department's
OL,10,FEffective Use of Resources (EUR)
OL,11,Fpolicy which states the specific
OL,12,Fcircumstances under which certain
OL,13,Fprocedures should be carried out.
OL,15,FOn average, more than 40 procedures
OL,16,Fwere carried out per day without
OL,17,Fassurance that they complied with
OL,18,Fgovernment policy.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
