OL,3,CConcerns raised over #22m 'restricted'
OL,4,Cprocedure spend in NI health service
OL,6,FThe report recommends that trusts
OL,7,Fintroduce procedures to ensure
OL,8,Fcompliance with the rules, and for
OL,9,Fincreased oversight and monitoring by
OL,10,Fthe Department of Health to make sure
OL,11,Fpolicy is being adhered to.
OL,13,FIt was also suggested that the policy
OL,14,Fitself be reviewed every two years.
OL,16,FIn response, the Department of Health
OL,17,Fand five health trusts said they will
OL,18,F"work to implement the
OL,19,Frecommendations".
